addSettingDeprecation(uint256,uint256,ad.details: Advocate of _creatorTAOId adds a setting deprecation

params._associatedTAOId: The taoId that the setting affects
params._creatorTAOId: The taoId that created the setting
params._newSettingContractAddress: The new setting contract address to route
params._newSettingId: The new setting ID to route
params._settingId: The ID of the setting to be deprecated

approveSettingDeprecation(uint256,bool).details: Advocate of SettingDeprecation's _associatedTAOId approves setting deprecation

params._settingId: The ID of the setting to approve

finalizeSettingDeprecation(uint256).details: Advocate of SettingDeprecation's _creatorTAOId finalizes the setting deprecation once the setting deprecation is approved

params._settingId: The ID of the setting to be finalized
